    {
      "card": {
        "bgColor": "var(--gray-3)",
        "label": "Lesson 8 • Discussing a difficult decision",
        "descriptions": [
          {
            "description": [
              {
                "text": "Anna, Lynn, and Jeff are thinking about moving their manufacturing facilities from the United States to China. Jeff is having trouble deciding what to do."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Jeff: "
            },
            {
              "text": "There are "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"pros and cons"
            },
            {
              "text":	" to moving it to China. I’ve been "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"back and forth "
            },
            {
              "text":	" on this issue for months. I’m "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"of two minds"
            },
            {
              "text":	"."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Anna: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Jeff, I know this is a "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"tough call"
            },
            {
              "text":	", but now is not the time to be "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"wishy-washy"
            },
            {
              "text":	". We need to make a decision."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Lyn: "
            },
            {
              "text": "That’s right, and I recommend we "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"bite the bullet"
            },
            {
              "text":	" and move our operations to China."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Anna: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Or we could "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"test the waters"
            },
            {
              "text":	" by moving 25 percent of our operations there."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Lynn: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Good idea. That would give us "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"the best of both worlds"
            },
            {
              "text":	": we could reduce our risk, while starting to enjoy some of the cost savings from lower-cost manufacturing."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Jeff: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I agree with you that we should "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"put a stake in the ground"
            },
            {
              "text":	". Let’s move a quarter of our operations to China."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Lynn: "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "Good call"
            },
            {
              "text":	", Jeff!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Jeff: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I hope I don’t "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"live to regret this decision"
            },
            {
              "text":	"."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Anna: "
            },
            {
              "text": "You won’t. "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"My gut tells me"
            },
            {
              "text":	" we’re doing the right thing."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
